fll-live-initscripts (2.0.68) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll_fshelper:
    - check if partition is in %p_seen hash when parsing /proc/mounts
    - remove usless block after checking %u_seen and %l_seen
    - use generic /media/disk{1..n} mount point names
    - unpack @_ in dbg function before processing its contents

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Thu, 29 Nov 2007 21:00:55 +1000

