fll-live-initscripts (1.2.1) unstable; urgency=low

  [ Stefan Lippers-Hollmann ]
  * revert r10116 and r10117 and make window manager selection more robust
    (again).

  [ Kel Modderman ]
  * Merge fll-fshelper functionality in form of bin/fll_fshelper.
  * Restructure top lovel files into bin/, lib/, man/ directories.
  * Add preinst with chroot check from udev/initramfs-tools. Package will fail
    to install in any system != chroot.
  * fll-fstab.init: update for /usr/sbin/fll_fshelper.
  * fll_fshelper: modularise ata_id usage.
  * fll_fshelper: no need to specify auto mount option when defaults is used.
  * fll_fshelper: improve MOUNTS loop.
  * fll-fstab.init: use --no-id option of fll_fshelper for live boot, faster.
  * fll_fshelper.8: update for --no-id, remove --no-swap short option.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Fri, 24 Aug 2007 20:30:31 +1000

