fll-live-initscripts (1.1.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * fll-cpufreq: no longer tamper with /etc/powersave/*, add cpufreq module to
    /etc/modules instead.
  * fll-locales: add kb field to locale headers that are parsed by sed for
    list argument. Output is install-gui friendly, and we only used sed once!
  * fll-network: try settling for one second rather than two when detecting
    link beat.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Tue, 26 Jun 2007 17:34:32 +1000

