    device.
  * fll-reboot: make "System halted" string green, to stand out against the
    yellow prompt to remove cd.
  * fll_login: ensure we are user friendly while creating ~/.hushlogin.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Mon, 04 Jun 2007 18:35:34 +1000

